            <title>香港 Donki 受 Windows 大死机影响，收银服务稍延长，只接受现金八达通、医管局未见异常</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/windows-shut-down-donki-cash-and-octopus-only/tech-secure/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=windows-shut-down-donki-cash-and-octopus-only</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/windows-shut-down-donki-cash-and-octopus-only/tech-secure/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 11:11:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[健康]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[资讯保安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电子支付]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[DON DON DONKI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Donki]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[windows]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[医管局]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1251586</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Windows 全球发生大规模蓝屏故障灾难，香港亦同样受到波及，香港机场部分航空公司受到影响需要改用人手办理登机手续，连锁超市「DON DON DONKI」亦同样受到影响。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1251587 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-34-694x419.jpg" alt="Donki" width="694" height="419" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-34-694x419.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-34.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9mIBOJyzpP/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link">dondondonkihk</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">DON DON DONKI 在 Facebook 和 Instagram 上发出公告，指由于系统故障收银服务时间将稍为延长，部分店舖目前只接受现金及八达通付款，即信用卡、WeChat Pay HK 和 AlipayHK 等多个付款方式都暂时无法在 Donki 使用。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1251594 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-13-e1721386142349-694x386.jpg" alt="医管局" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-13-e1721386142349-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-13-e1721386142349-1280x712.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-13-e1721386142349.jpg 1524w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1750944-20240428.htm">RTHK</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">医管局指留意到 Windows 系统故障影响全球，已检查医管局的电脑系统，目前未有发现任何异常。医管局表示会密切留意情况，确保公立医院和病人服务不会受到影响。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2012093/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E6%AD%BB%E6%A9%9F%EF%B8%B1DONKI%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%BA%97%E8%88%96%E5%8F%AA%E6%94%B6%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A-%E9%86%AB%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E6%9C%AA%E6%9C%89%E7%95%B0%E5%B8%B8?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR1AkiV6JhMPrulIed8ySiH2htHH7fgvNNkeAUF0B-z9qjpoT_GNi451hmM_aem_4Bq8Wccvf3yrIvhu2ts4KA">星岛</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9mIBOJyzpP/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link">dondondonkihk</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/27/senuas-saga-hellblade-ii-review/game-channel/game-review/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】《Senua&#8217;s Saga: Hellblade II》 精神病主题黑暗风格</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/20/msi-claw-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】MSI Claw　外形　手感　效能　打机体验　散热　屏幕 5 大优点 + 缺点开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/windows-blue-screen/tech-secure/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">全球广泛 Windows 用户面对蓝屏，疑似一款防毒软件累事</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/windows-shut-down-donki-cash-and-octopus-only/tech-secure/">香港 Donki 受 Windows 大死机影响，收银服务稍延长，只接受现金八达通、医管局未见异常</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
