        <item>
            <title>【教学】CrowdStrike 让 Windows blue screen 蓝屏开不到机解决方法</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/windows-blue-screen-%e8%97%8d%e5%b1%8f%e9%96%8b%e4%b8%8d%e5%88%b0%e6%a9%9f%e8%a7%a3%e6%b1%ba%e6%96%b9%e6%b3%95%e6%95%99%e5%ad%b8-%e5%88%aa%e9%99%a4%e6%9c%89%e5%95%8f%e9%a1%8c%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=windows-blue-screen-%25e8%2597%258d%25e5%25b1%258f%25e9%2596%258b%25e4%25b8%258d%25e5%2588%25b0%25e6%25a9%259f%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e6%25b1%25ba%25e6%2596%25b9%25e6%25b3%2595%25e6%2595%2599%25e5%25ad%25b8-%25e5%2588%25aa%25e9%2599%25a4%25e6%259c%2589%25e5%2595%258f%25e9%25a1%258c%25e6%2596%2587%25e4%25bb%25b6</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/windows-blue-screen-%e8%97%8d%e5%b1%8f%e9%96%8b%e4%b8%8d%e5%88%b0%e6%a9%9f%e8%a7%a3%e6%b1%ba%e6%96%b9%e6%b3%95%e6%95%99%e5%ad%b8-%e5%88%aa%e9%99%a4%e6%9c%89%e5%95%8f%e9%a1%8c%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 08:12:35 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1251473</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在 7 月 19 日一款名为 CrowdStrike 的防毒软件引起全球 Windows 灾难，因为好多厂机都安装了这款应用程式。全球多国用家面对 Windows 开机出现蓝屏的问题。有专家就建议几个步骤，如果电脑中招，可以跟著这些步骤解决问题。</p><p>消息指 CrowdStrike 工程部已经确定与此问题相关的内容部署，现在用家可依照以下步骤解决问题：</p><h2>将 Windows 进入安全模式或 Windows 恢复环境。</h2><p>（如电脑开机黑画面或入不到 Windows，「开机见到手提电脑开机画面（如电脑厂 logo）长按电源按钮 10 秒关机＞开电源按钮一下开机＞见到手提电脑开机画面长按电源按钮 10 秒关机＞开电源按钮一下开机＞见到手提电脑开机画面长按电源按钮 10 秒关机」让电脑认识你多次开机失败，之后再次开机就可进入图中的选单画面）详细可参考这个 <a href="https://support.microsoft.com/zh-hk/windows/在-windows-中以安全模式启动电脑-92c27cff-db89-8644-1ce4-b3e5e56fe234">Windows 支援页面</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251479" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1088-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1088-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1088-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲开机后选 Troubleshoot</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251481" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_10892-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_10892-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_10892-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择 Advanced options</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251482" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1091-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1091-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1091-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲按 Restart 重新启动电脑</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251483" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1092-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1092-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1092-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在重启电脑后的「启动设定」选单选「5) 启用安全模式 (含网路功能)」</p><p>在开启安全模式后，利用档案总管打开 C:\Windows\System32\drivers\CrowdStrike 目录。找到符合 &#8220;C-00000291*.sys&#8221; 的文件，并删除它。最后正常启动主机便可回复原状。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/crowdstrike/comments/1e6vmkf/bsod_error_in_latest_crowdstrike_update/">Reddit</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/windows-blue-screen-%e8%97%8d%e5%b1%8f%e9%96%8b%e4%b8%8d%e5%88%b0%e6%a9%9f%e8%a7%a3%e6%b1%ba%e6%96%b9%e6%b3%95%e6%95%99%e5%ad%b8-%e5%88%aa%e9%99%a4%e6%9c%89%e5%95%8f%e9%a1%8c%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6/fun-tech/">【教学】CrowdStrike 让 Windows blue screen 蓝屏开不到机解决方法</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
