        <item>
            <title>加强版多啦 A 梦无人机汇演明晚再现维港，官方公布最佳观赏位置</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/doraemon100-tour-in-hk-again/hottopic/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=doraemon100-tour-in-hk-again</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/doraemon100-tour-in-hk-again/hottopic/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 06:24:15 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活娱乐]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[航拍]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[叮当]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[多啦 A 梦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[无人机汇演]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1251418</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">全球首场多啦 A 梦无人机汇演早前于 5 月 25 日在香港上演，反应非常热烈并宣布举行第二次汇演。官方称是次汇演为「加强版」，加入了新登场的彩蛋画面和惊喜互动，乘坐着时光机的多啦 A 梦将与一众好友再度出现在维港上空。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1251419 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451808512_1008884457-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451808512_1008884457-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451808512_1008884457.jpg 719w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/100Doraemon/posts/1008891260633939">Doraemon 100</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">汇演将于明晚 7:30 pm 尖东维港上空举行，预计表演内容大约 10 分钟，官方更公开了汇演的最佳观赏位置。表演当晚尖东将实施封路及人流管制措施，将会封闭梳士巴利道部分行车路段（东行及西行）和附近一带的道路。大会建议市民可以到两个最佳观赏位置，分别是尖沙咀海滨公园（尖东海傍）以及封闭后的梳士巴利道（东行）部分行车路段。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1251420 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451436245_1008884537-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451436245_1008884537-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451436245_1008884537.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/100Doraemon/posts/1008891260633939">Doraemon 100 </a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">天文台正考虑今日下午至晚上发出一号戒备信号，明晚的多啦 A 梦无人机汇演亦有机会因天气关系受到影响，有计划观赏汇演的大家一定要密切留意官方在 <a href="https://www.facebook.com/100Doraemon">Facebook</a> 和 <a href="https://www.instagram.com/doraemon100_tour/">Instagram</a> 上的最新消息。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E7%86%B1%E9%BB%9E/article/20240719/s00024/1720523239251/%E5%A4%9A%E5%95%A6a%E5%A4%A2%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E5%8C%AF%E6%BC%94%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E7%89%887%E6%9C%8820%E6%97%A5%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C-%E5%A4%9A%E5%95%A6a%E5%A4%A2%E4%B9%98%E6%99%82%E5%85%89%E6%A9%9F%E7%8F%BE%E5%B0%96%E6%9D%B1%E5%A4%9C%E7%A9%BA%E3%80%90%E9%99%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E8%A7%80%E8%B3%9E%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%91?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR3KdFobUX7feNRK-LH4oHrUw4JvHAlkyCPSo7nea3t2EdmzSplBN5Nf7Iw_aem_ESztLzvSLlcaqknRVAetBw">明报</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/100Doraemon/videos/993424982379583/">Doraemon 100</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/05/doraemon-4/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">多啦 A 梦无人机汇演「加强版」　新内容及彩蛋 +表演日期</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/28/doraemon-3/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">江玉欢：无人机表演比烟火更具潜力，可在背景较暗的环境进行</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/doraemon100-tour-in-hk-again/hottopic/">加强版多啦 A 梦无人机汇演明晚再现维港，官方公布最佳观赏位置</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
