        <item>
            <title>Diablo IV 新资料片《憎恨之躯》初步试玩心得分享 :　「魂灵师」玩法超多变</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/vessel-of-hatred-preview/game-channel/game-review/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=vessel-of-hatred-preview</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/vessel-of-hatred-preview/game-channel/game-review/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[天恩]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 05:15:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏评测]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1251314</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小编有幸率先体验《暗黑破坏神 4》（Diablo IV）最新资料片《憎恨之躯》（Vessel of Hatred）及全新职业「魂灵师」（Spiritborn）。现在就为大家分享一下这次重大 DLC 的新职业、地图及心得。</p><h2><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0345-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251392" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0345-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0345-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0345-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></h2><h2>相关短片:</h2><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="Diablo IV 新资料片《憎恨之躯》初步试玩心得分享" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/986969305?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/diablo-iv-3/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《Diablo IV》新资料片  Vessel of Hatred 专访，游戏总监: 教你魂灵师如何搭配「最强伤害组合」</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/diablo-iv-2/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《Diablo IV》新资料片 Vessel of Hatred 新职业: 魂灵师，如同随时「转职」 坦、法、僧侣、侠盗集一身</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/diablo-iv-vessel-of-hatred/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Diablo IV 首个资料片 10 月推出　《憎恨之躯》将加入新职业和地图等</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>「魂灵师」　尤如四合一新职业</h2><p>「魂灵师」这个新职业可以召唤四种魂灵守护者：蜈蚣、巨猩、猎豹及飞鹰。每种守护者都有其特色和技能树，玩家可以选择两个来获得其被动加成。试玩了四个预设的魂灵师，等级限制在 30 级。虽未能体验后期内容，但初步感受良好。以下是对每个守护者建构的简单评价：</p><p><strong>蜈蚣，试玩感</strong></p><p>主打持续伤害（DOT），可同时造成伤害及治疗自身。笔者最喜爱的一个，持续伤害的玩法流畅，技能效果华丽，感觉非常强大。不过整个画面都是毒绿色及「特别」音效就不是每个人都喜欢。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114910.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251385" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114910-694x427.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="427" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114910-694x427.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114910.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="魂灵守护者「蜈蚣」技能施放预览" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/986427384?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><strong>巨猩，试玩感</strong></p><p>偏向防御，拥有高坦度和反击能力，适合喜爱肉盾玩法的玩家。防御力和反击能力极高，游玩时宛如一个野蛮人坦克。出招时感觉到地震是四款之中打击感最强的。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122527.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251406" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122527-694x410.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="410" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122527-694x410.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122527.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="魂灵守护者「巨猩」技能施放预览" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/986426813?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><strong>猎豹，试玩感</strong></p><p>专注于快速多次打击和高机动性，类似潜行者的玩法。机动性高，打击速度快，因为需要堆叠大招所以要不停清怪，玩起来节奏感强又爽，但缺点是防太低易死，solo 不太建议用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122237.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251405" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122237-694x464.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122237-694x464.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122237.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="魂灵守护者「猎豹」技能施放预览" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/986427697?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br /><strong>飞鹰，试玩感</strong></p><p>擅长中距离攻击，有来回飞行的羽毛攻击技能。但相较其他三个守护者，感觉略逊一筹，令我想起法师 teleport ，技能多数针对单体伤害，用来打小王及 boss 比较合适，反为依靠大招范围清小怪</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115241.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251381" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115241-694x418.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="418" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115241-694x418.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115241.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="魂灵守护者「飞鹰」技能施放预览" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/986427020?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><h2>技能混合才是精綷</h2><p>每个魂灵守护者都有独特技能和装备搭配，玩法多变，玩家可以混合不同守护者的技能，创造出独特的建构。笔者尝试了混合不同魂灵守护者的技能。将蜈蚣的持续伤害技能与巨猩的高防御技能结合，可以创造出一个既能造成大量伤害又非常耐打的角色。这样的组合让你在面对大量敌人时仍能保持生存，并且逐渐削弱敌人。</p><p>我同时试了「强攻」型将猎豹混合蜈蚣，清怪超快但要份外小心，因为「皮薄」需要留意血量，小编用这个组合经常要饮红水。如果不作混合，也可能主副选相同的魂灵去大大强化本身特色。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114622.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251376" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114622-555x580.jpg" alt="" width="555" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114622-555x580.jpg 555w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114622.jpg 861w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 555px" /></a></p><h2>终极技能及新机制</h2><p>每个魂灵守护者都有其独特的终极技能大招（Ultimate），无论是巨猩的持续伤害和屏障，还是猎豹的高速攻击和重置冷却时间，都令游戏过程更加丰富。魂灵师还引入了几个新机制：</p><p>决心（Resolve）：增强防御的效果，每受到一次伤害就会失去一层，但只要还有层数，就能提供 20% 的伤害减免。<br />
不受阻碍（Unhindered）：可穿越敌人，移动速度不会被减慢。<br />
狂怒（Ferocity）：增加攻击速度的效果，可叠加。</p><p>基本上这个设定逼使玩家要主动出击才能获得最大得著，如果在团中瑟缩一角对保命力和输出都大打节扣，是高风险高回报的玩法，比较适合节奏明快的玩家</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115850.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251378" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115850-429x580.jpg" alt="" width="429" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115850-429x580.jpg 429w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115850.jpg 665w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 429px" /></a></p><h2>新地图视觉效果出色</h2><p>除了魂灵师，小编还体验一些新区域和据点。视觉效果非常出色，尤其是一个充满灯笼和光影对比强烈的据点令人印象深刻。玩家需要携带灯笼照亮黑暗区域，并在战斗中利用光照机制对付敌人，大大增加了游戏的策略性和趣味性。这种气氛已经令你回想起 Diablo 2 ，同时你又真的听到一些 D2 怀旧 BGM，令老玩家倍感亲切。</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/diablo-iv-3/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《Diablo IV》新资料片  Vessel of Hatred 专访，游戏总监: 教你魂灵师如何搭配「最强伤害组合」</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/diablo-iv-2/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《Diablo IV》新资料片 Vessel of Hatred 新职业: 魂灵师，如同随时「转职」 坦、法、僧侣、侠盗集一身</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/diablo-iv-vessel-of-hatred/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Diablo IV 首个资料片 10 月推出　《憎恨之躯》将加入新职业和地图等</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>总结 : 值得再次投入</h2><p>整体而言，魂灵师这个新职业带来了全新的游戏机制，多样性和灵活性极高。玩家可以根据自己的喜好，自由搭配不同的魂灵守护者技能，创造出独特且强大的建构。感觉就像是四个新职业合而为一，每个守护者都有其独特风格和玩法。<br />
虽然这次只体验到前期内容，但已令人期待满满。如果你对这个新职业感兴趣，不妨等待更多资讯发布后再作决定。</p><h1 style="text-align: center;"></h1><div style="padding:56.25% 0 0 0;position:relative;"><iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/986969305?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;" title="Diablo IV 新资料片《憎恨之躯》初步试玩心得分享"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><h2>后记: 总部参观充满游戏色彩</h2><p>除了试玩小编还参观暴雪总部，馆内的大型雕像令人印象深刻，还有专门的博物馆展示游戏开发历程。目前展示的是《Warcraft Rumble》的内容，此前曾展出《暗黑破坏神 4》的相关资料。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0320-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251399" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0320-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0320-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0320-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0324-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251398" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0324-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0324-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0324-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0348-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251396" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0348-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0348-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0348-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0346-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251397" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0346-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0346-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0346-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0357-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251395" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0357-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0357-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0357-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/diablo-iv-3/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《Diablo IV》新资料片  Vessel of Hatred 专访，游戏总监: 教你魂灵师如何搭配「最强伤害组合」</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/diablo-iv-2/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《Diablo IV》新资料片 Vessel of Hatred 新职业: 魂灵师，如同随时「转职」 坦、法、僧侣、侠盗集一身</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/diablo-iv-vessel-of-hatred/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Diablo IV 首个资料片 10 月推出　《憎恨之躯》将加入新职业和地图等</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/vessel-of-hatred-preview/game-channel/game-review/">Diablo IV 新资料片《憎